   Lukens has denied the charge and said he was the victim of a
``setup'' by the girl, who he said was seeking money.
   The indictment came after a television station broadcast a
secretly recorded videotape in which the girl's mother asked Lukens
why he was ``messin' around'' with her teen-age daughter. Lukens
replied that he did not know the girl was a teen-ager, the station
said.
