index was 4.9 points, or 0.2 percent, higher at 2,088.4, and below
its midmorning best level of 2,092.1. The index began the day at its
2,085.5 low point.
   Volume amounted to a modest 324 million shares by midday,
compared with 357.1 million shares at the same time Tuesday.
